# {{.Type}} ({{.Name}})

{{ .Description | trimspace }}

This data source provides detailed information about a specific application family, including all available countries/regions and their supported rings. Use this when you need information about a single application family rather than listing all available families.

## Example Usage

### Basic Usage

{{tffile "examples/data-sources/bc_admin_center_application_family/data-source.tf"}}

### Using Output in Environment Resource

```terraform
data "bcadmincenter_application_family" "bc" {
  name = "BusinessCentral"
}

# Use the data to find available countries
output "available_countries" {
  value = [for country in data.bcadmincenter_application_family.bc.countries_ring_details : country.country_code]
}

# Create an environment using data from the application family
resource "bcadmincenter_environment" "example" {
  name                = "production-env"
  application_family  = data.bcadmincenter_application_family.bc.name
  country_code        = data.bcadmincenter_application_family.bc.countries_ring_details[0].country_code
  ring_name           = data.bcadmincenter_application_family.bc.countries_ring_details[0].rings[0].name
  type                = "Production"
  application_version = "24.0"
}
```

{{ .SchemaMarkdown | trimspace }}

## Use Cases

This data source is useful when you need to:

- Query available countries/regions for a specific application family
- Find available rings for environment creation
- Discover production vs. preview rings for a specific country/region
- Dynamically configure environment resources based on available options

